/*Recommended node ID allocation
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-ID-	-Node Type-
0	- Special allocation in JeeLib RFM12 driver - reserved for OOK use
1-4     - Control nodes
5-10	- Energy monitoring nodes
11-14	--Un-assigned --
